title: Blue Sky Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A breakfast, lunch, and coffee place that accommodates vegan diets. In addition to the vegan options listed on the menu, staff will substitute tofu for eggs in the egg dishes. Example: replace eggs with tofu in the Santa Fe Huevos. Large selection of smoothies, fresh juices, and coffee drinks with soy milk available. Uses biodegradable carry out containers and utensils.
